4. Use champion/challenger where challenger is market-implied (perp basis, options skew, borrow stress) to catch model-blind on-chain signals.

**Bottom line**
The proposal improves credibility and sequencing, but it still undershoots the main architectural mismatch. It works as a risk radar pitch, not as a defensible credit-rating framework, unless the target variable and validation regime are redefined.

